{"tid":1779003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"記者搵人 Journalist in search of a former contact","createTime":"2019-12-11T11:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T11:32:32.000Z","uid":270274,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"861cac76be040dc02077af586010d3c8a5c06827","tid":1779003,"uid":270274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T11:09:46.000Z","msg":"Hello, I'm the US journalist you contacted when I was seeking protesters to interview this summer. You were going to write to me about what you witnessed one day. (You also left a voice message for me.) Please reach out if you see this post, and indicate the name you used this summer, your first social movement, and where you witnessed the event you described below. Of course I will protect your identity, and no, I won't photograph or take videos.<br />\nHere is the message you sent me:<br />\nI witnessed clearly that the police stormed into xxxx. They fired tear gas towards the crowd at horizon angle. And when I was there, I saw a protestor who got hit right in his face by the police. He immediately fainted and was unconscious.<br />\nHere is my press credential:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3yzO4u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3yzO4u.jpg&h=24b140b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPlease contact me when you see my post, thank you!"},{"pid":"dfb1d9bab6d184d444b56659895b20c18e88a677","tid":1779003,"uid":160650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T11:12:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65c400351c6668bd74919dffcc7b813f95cab557","tid":1779003,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T11:13:19.000Z","msg":"請推po<br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cb52a264eb7e88b64d44b427f86d42e3ff75f223","tid":1779003,"uid":9346,"like":0,"disli